                     <interp inst="t18300415-323-off1760" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300415-323-off1760" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the 13th of March, 1 watch, value 1l.; 1 seal, value 3s.; 2 watch-keys, value 2s.; 1 ring, value 2d., and 1 watch-ribbon, value 1d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18300415-323-victim2699" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Walker
                        <interp inst="t18300415-323-victim2699" type="surname" value="Walker"></interp>
